reviewText: Yo this is where it all started from. Pick up this DVD and get ya game hotter than a flame ya dig? There's a lot of imposters but CCP 1-5 will open ya mind to one of the oldest grinds..
This was a great film.  Watching the balls all over the country and the life style

I loved this dvd because it kept it all the way real and showed the lifestyle of Pimping and Hoe'n how it was in the late 90's and early 2000. My favorite scene was when Ka$hanova (an ex pimp out of San Diego) was explaining his situation and what lead him to go on the run for 5 years. Nice job on this one
Excellent documentary. It feels like you go on a ride. The entire film you feel like you actually go to all the places and events Cross Country. An eye opening documentary.
